title: Dominoes: Part 4
description: Several unexpected events occur and truths are revealed as this final pattern of fallen dominoes reveals itself. Will Sally be found? Can Laney be taken from the only home she's ever known? Are the accusations against Jenna valid? Read on to answer these questions and others as Dominoes winds its way to the end.  All characters in this novel are fictional and any similarity to a living person is completely coincidental.
author: C.B. Blaha
